Kim, Ron and Rufus have been trapped by Dr Drakken in a factory. Now they must find the three hidden nachos so that Ron can burp their way to freedom. Use each of the character's hidden powers to unlock the secret nachos!

  * Kim can fire pellets that dispel tornadoes. Beware! Running into a tornado will return the active character to the start position on the map
  * Ron can fire-burp through walls
  * Rufus can run on hamster wheels, illuminating hidden areas on the map

Press enter to go past the intro screen.

Press 1, 2, or 3 to cycle through characters.

Use the arrow keys to move. The up key helps the character jump to the platform above the current one. 

The spacebar will use each character's special power.

Good luck beating the game!